query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('backup',
'complex-geometry',
'computability',
'education',
'lightdm',
'problem-solving',
'security',
'ubuntu-touch',
'uniform-convergence',
'uninstall',
'volume',
'windows-10')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name ilike '%teach%'
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
